  "name": "paper_eval",
  "role": "main",
  "description": "Unified benchmark-spec manifest for the MICAD paper. This encodes the paper's required Sachs evaluation cells together with the six-graph names-only floor. Because benchmark_specs apply prompt_cells globally across datasets, this manifest is a conservative superset of the paper's minimum run plan.",
